  "text": "Let us recall that the rigidly traveling Supersonic and Superluminal solutions found in refs. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] and in this paper -some of them already experimentally realizedappear to be (generally speaking) X-shaped, just as predicted in 1982 by Barut, Maccarrone and Recami [CITATION_3] .",
